scron
=====

about
-----
simple cron daemon

features
--------
schedule tasks
single daemon, config and initscript
log job output: command &>> /var/log/cron.log
run as different user: su -c 'command' user
log to stdout and syslog
no mail support

config
------
syntax:
value: * (wildcard), 30 (number) or 1-5 (range)
separator: \t (tab)

example:
# tm_min tm_hour tm_mday tm_mon tm_wday command
# 6:00 every day
0	6	*	*	*	updatedb
# 5:30 every weekday
30	5	*	*	1-5	rsync -r --quiet /var/www backup@192.168.0.8:~
